description: Manage metric statistics for AFD profile.

commands.name: az afd log-analytic metric list
commands.summary: Get log report for AFD profile.
commands.syntax:
az afd log-analytic metric list --custom-domains
                                --date-time-begin
                                --date-time-end
                                --granularity {P1D, PT1H, PT5M}
                                --metrics
                                --profile-name
                                --protocols
                                --resource-group
                                [--continents]
                                [--country-or-regions]
                                [--group-by]
